title: Elvis Presley - Pure diamonds box -4cd- (2007)
description:
Title:  Pure Diamonds - The Uncut & Undubbed RCA Studio Sessions   
  Label:  WLR   
  Label Number:  2018   
  Release Date:  2007   
  Recording Type:  Studio   
  Location:  Hollywood / Nashville and Memphis   
  Date:  Various   
  Sound:  Excellent   
          
  Track Listing:   Disc 1:

 Almost In Love - If I Were You - Only Believe - Mary In The Morning - You Don't Have To Say You Love Me - I'll Never Know - Just Pretend - Life - Stranger In The Crowd - This Is Our Dance - Heart Of Rome - It's Your Baby , You Rock It - First Time Ever I Saw Your Face - Help Me Make It Trough The Night - Until It's Time For You To Go - It's Only Love - We Can Make The Morning.
 Bonus Track: Britches.

 Disc 2:

 When I'm Over You - Make The World Go Away - Funny How Time Slips Away - Snowbird - Where Did They Go Lord ? - Rags To Riches - The Sound Of Your Cry - I Washed My Hands In Muddy Water - Patch It Up - It Ain't No Big Thing - Bridge Over Troubled Water - Cindy Cindy - Got My Mojo Working.

 Disc 3:

 Put Your Hand In The Hand - Reach Out To Jesus - He Is My Everything - There Is No God But God - I , John - Bosom Of Abraham - Put Your Hand In The Hand - Raised On Rock - Just A Little Bit - If You Don't Come Back - Three Corn Patches - Take Good Care Of Her - Find Out What's Happening - I've Got A Thing About You Baby - Just A Little Bit - For Ol' Times Sake - Raised On Rock.

 Disc 4:

 Twenty Days And Twenty Nights - I've Lost You - I Was Born About Ten Thousand Years Ago - The Sound Of Your Cry - The Fool - Little Cabin On The Hill - Cindy , Cindy - Bridge Over Troubled Water - Got My Mojo Working - How The Web Was Woven - The First Time Ever I Saw Your Face - Untill It's Time For You To Go - Separate Ways - For The Good Times - Where Do I Go From Here - Burning Love - Fool - Always On My Mind - It's A Matter Of Time - For The Good Times - Untill It's Time For You To Go.
     
Note:   All songs are undubbed versions !
  
 All songs can be found on the Pure Diamonds series from Flashback !

Box has a 24 page booklet inside ! 


Enjoy!
